  "text": "# GENERAL QUESTIONS  \n## About FirstUK Bank  \n**Q: What is FirstUK Bank?**\nA: FirstUK Bank is a UK retail bank offering savings accounts, current accounts, and mortgages. We're committed to competitive rates, transparent pricing, and excellent customer service.  \n**Q: Where is FirstUK Bank based?**\nA: We're headquartered in London with 12 branches across the UK (London, Manchester, Leeds, Birmingham, Bristol, Edinburgh, Glasgow, Liverpool, Norwich, Southampton, and Belfast).  \n**Q: Is my money safe with FirstUK Bank?**\nA: Yes. We're regulated by the FCA and PRA. Your deposits are protected by the Financial Services Compensation Scheme (FSCS) up to £85,000.  \n**Q: How do I contact FirstUK Bank?**\nA:\n- **Phone:** 0800-555-2265 (Mon–Fri 08:00–20:00, Sat 09:00–17:00)\n- **Email:** support@firstuk.bank\n- **Branch:** Visit any of our 12 locations\n- **Online Chat:** Available at www.firstuk.bank (business hours)  \n**Q: Does FirstUK Bank offer business banking?**\nA: Currently, we focus on retail banking. Business accounts are on our roadmap for 2027.  \n---",
